/image_924925656.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/924925656/image_924925656.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/924925656/image_924925656.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/924925656/image_924925656.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/924925656/image_924925656.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/924925656/image_924925656.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/924925656/image_924925656.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SIphotography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Advent Convertible &amp; Income Fund (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVK\" title=\"Advent Convertible &amp; Income Fund\">AVK</a></span>) is an income fund that offers the potential for long-term upside with its significant allocation in convertible issues. With a history of a steadily growing yield and price putting it at 12%, we</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/924925656/image_924925656.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745581-avk-good-income-but-credit-concerns", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:54:37", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745604", "title": "Winnebago Industries, Inc. 2025 Q1 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Winnebago Industries, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q1 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-pr