-emerging-markets-equity-advantage-portfolio-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:25:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745591", "title": "Party On", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Presidential Election Betting\" data-id=\"2181544373\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Douglas Rissing</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Things are not as dismal as some think. The reaction to the Fed\u2019s announcement of their last cut and the expectations that surrounded it whacked the market on Wednesday as if the future had dimmed significantly. There was probably</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745591-party-on", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:20:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}]}